sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LB as LoadBalancer /<br/>OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EnvoyFilter as EnvoyFilter<br/>ext_authz
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth /<br/>OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Backend App<br/>(via HTTPRoute)

    Note over Client,Backend: Flow 1: External User → Gateway → Application

    Client->>LB: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+
    LB->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS terminate/reencrypt
    Gateway->>EnvoyFilter: Route matching
    EnvoyFilter->>AuthProxy: ext_authz check<br/>HTTPS/8443 (service-ca TLS)<br/>Cookie or Bearer token
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: Validate credentials<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>OAuth2/OIDC
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Auth response
    AuthProxy-->>EnvoyFilter: Auth decision
    EnvoyFilter->>Backend: Lua filter injects<br/>Authorization header<br/>strips cookies
    Backend-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON/HTML Response

    Note over Client,Backend: Flow 2: Component Lifecycle Management

    participant Admin as Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller

    Admin->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DSC CR<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>kubeconfig auth
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount token
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create component CRs<br/>Server-Side Apply (SSA)
    K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch notification
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply kustomize manifests<br/>SSA with field ownership

    Note over Client,Backend: Flow 3: Monitoring Telemetry Collection

    participant AppPod as Application Pod
    participant OTelCol as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant Tempo as Tempo<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant MonStack as MonitoringStack<br/>(Prometheus)
    participant Thanos as ThanosQuerier<br/>9090/TCP

    AppPod->>OTelCol: OTLP traces<br/>gRPC/4317<br/>Optional TLS
    OTelCol->>Tempo: Forward traces<br/>gRPC/4317<br/>Optional TLS
    MonStack->>AppPod: Scrape metrics<br/>HTTP (ServiceMonitor)
    MonStack->>Thanos: Query federation<br/>HTTP/9090<br/>TLS (service-ca)
